room_title: Escape room "Zombie Apocalypse" by Tampa Bay Escape Room in Tampa
room_description: You are seeking safety from the devastated streets inside this house. You now realize you are not alone and not only do you need to save yourselves but a little girl as well. Will you gain entrance thought the front door before you get bitten? Will you save the little girl in time? Hurry, the clock is ticking!
